node.text:
Next week, I’m going to start periodically publishing my perspectives on current events — uncensored, memorialized to the Blockchain and made available to own, collect, tout and trade as NFTs by freedom lovers like you. Link in bio.

I’m calling it The Non-Fungible Freedom Column.

You can think of this as my version of a New Yorker magazine cover — just with a bit more sarcasm, truth & freedom. ;)

node.text:
There are 4 other individuals with Mr. Gates at “Plandemic Mtg #4” (my first NFT). Who do you think they are?

ABOUT THIS PIECE.
“Plandemic Mtg #4” (1/1) will be auctioned off next week on Opensea as the first NFT in a collection entitled, The Non-Fungible Freedom Column. The winner of the auction will also win a role in one of my comedy videos, VIP tickets to a comedy show and a merch care package curated by yours truly! Learn more @ Freedom Column link in bio.

ABOUT THIS NFT COLLECTION.
The Non-Fungible Freedom Column is where I am periodically publishing my perspectives on current events — uncensored, memorialized to the Blockchain and made available to own, collect, tout and trade as NFTs by freedom lovers. Learn more @ Freedom Column link in bio.

node.text:

I’m calling it The Non-Fungible Freedom Column.

You can think of this as my version of a New Yorker magazine cover — just with a bit more sarcasm, truth & freedom. ;)
